      "body" : "I've seen no evidence that this edge case is at all rare. That really sounds like an unsubstantiated claim. We do want your average non-techie to be able to use Armory, right?\r\n\r\nAnyways, printing out the leveldb error verbatim sounds like a perfectly fine solution to me. As long as errors aren't pages long, people read em, and if the solution to the problem is written right there in the error (like it seems to be in this case) then great!",
